title: Femininomenon

description.plain:
“Femininomenon” is a combination of “feminine” and “phenomenon”. Chappell created the word because it was “a phenomenon if sleeping with a man was better than sleeping with a girl”.

She expanded on this in a Reddit comment:

“ummm no man could literally get me off (stilll the case ᵔᴥᵔ) and my cowriter and i were just messing around and made up the word haha! it’s so weird”
